IMPORTANT: This repository contains processed data from the MinhQND Dictionary project (https://github.com/minhqnd/dictionary), which itself compiles data from multiple open-source linguistic resources.

**Contributors to this version:**
- Skypedia (github.com/skypediacode, 2026) – Database processing, example sentences, SQLite optimization
- minhqnd (https://github.com/minhqnd/dictionary) – Original dictionary compilation and structure

**Upstream open-source linguistic resources (via MinhQND Dictionary):**
- Wiktionary (https://www.wiktionary.org) – CC BY-SA license
- vntk/dictionary – CC BY-SA license
- Hồ Ngọc Đức's Vietnamese Dictionary Project – Open-source Vietnamese lexical data
- WikDict and open-dict-data (https://github.com/open-dict-data/ipa-dict) – CC BY-SA licenses

